 barbeque set, gaskets, cleaning tools, ladders, dust bin, copper water dispenser, and gas lighter; and wedding gift. The company sells its products through a network of outlets under the Prestige Xclusive name; and online. TTK Prestige Limited was incorporated in 1955 and is headquartered in Bengaluru, India."}}